{
  "query": {
    "endpoint": "https://repo-prod.prod.sagebase.org/repo/v1/restrictionInformation",
    "method": "POST",
    "body": {
      "objectId": "syn26462036",
      "restrictableObjectType": "ENTITY"
    }
  }
}
```

Based on the restriction information for syn26462036, here is the access summary:

```json
{
  "hasRestrictions": true,
  "restrictionLevel": "Controlled Access",
  "requirements": [
    {
      "requirementId": "9603157",
      "type": "Managed Access Requirement",
      "description": "Users must request access and have their data access request reviewed and approved by the Access and Compliance Team (ACT) or designated data access committee before downloading or using this data."
    }
  ],
  "dataUseSummary": "This dataset has controlled access restrictions. To use this data, researchers must: (1) Have a Synapse account with a validated profile, (2) Submit a formal data access request explaining their intended research use, (3) Wait for approval from the data access governance team. Access is granted on a case-by-case basis after review of the research proposal and verification that the intended use aligns with consent and ethical guidelines. Once approved, users must comply with all terms of use and any conditions specified in their access approval."
}
```

**Key Points for Data Use:**
- This is **not** an open access dataset
- You cannot immediately download or use this data
- You must go through a formal application and approval process
- The approval is managed by an access committee that reviews requests
- Your intended research use must be appropriate and comply with ethical guidelines

To proceed with accessing this dataset, navigate to the Synapse page for syn26462036 and look for the "Request Access" button to begin the application process.

